run away.

âFat deil ails her?â cries the lieutenant.

And suddenly engaging, he twitched the sword out of my grasp and sent it
flying far among the rushes.

Twice was this manÅuvre repeated; and the third time when I brought back
my humiliated weapon, I found he had returned his own to the scabbard,
