Day cam, there were the rousing compainions, and his guid resolves
depairtit.

In thir days, dwalled upon the Bass a man of God, Peden the Prophet was
his name.  Yeâll have heard tell of Prophet Peden.  There was never the
wale of him sinsyne, and itâs a question wiâ mony if there ever was his
