âShe would ken that story afore,â he said.  âShe was the story of Uistean
More MâGillie Phadrig and the Gavar Vore.â

âIt is no sic a thing,â cried Andie.  âIt is the story of my faither (now
wiâ God) and Tod Lapraik.  And the same in your beard,â says he; âand
